data.title: Nixon with Egyptian President Gamal Abdel Nasser
data.meta_description: Cairo: The late Egyptian President Gamal Abdel Nasser (R) is shown talking with Richard Nixon, then out of office and touring the Middle East, in this 6/23/63 photo. Nasser died after suffering a heart attack 9/28.
